dcterms:description: The first Multi-class, Class-Agnostic Counting dataset designed to facilitate the development and evaluation of counting methods in multi-class settings. It contains images with between 1 and 4 classes of objects and up to 300 instances per class, with associated labels and bounding boxes.
dcterms:title: MCAC (Multi-class Class-Agnostic Counting dataset)

dcterms:creator: V. Ranjan
